{"tid":937824,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"冬天富良野無車可以點玩一日？","createTime":"2018-12-11T23:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T10:18:59.000Z","uid":36492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00cd204cbfba25606a88546fbc0c1a12da2aed43","tid":937824,"uid":36492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:06:20.000Z","msg":"家庭旅行一月出發<br />\n個陣未睇資料就book左兩日係富良野<br />\n有一日住滑雪場酒店，滑雪為主唔多擔心無節目<br />\n另外一日就住富良野站隔離間酒店，未有行程<br />\n上網睇左好多local tour，唔多fit<br />\n睇啱既有熱氣球，雪橇拉車，夜晚青池點燈<br />\n<br />\n但係熱氣球兩老話驚危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算<br />\n<br />\n雪橇拉車幾好既但係個地點係南富良野再遠好多<br />\n佢又無車接送，我地又唔係自駕遊，去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩番個啲吸引既一日遊tour，全部都係札幌市出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好後悔擺左兩日係到，有無高手打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d17dbda97c78112057dd6f950589c96b692d26","tid":937824,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:45:25.000Z","msg":"你食唔食得涼野"},{"pid":"542a2f582e8ea1bf20b1b4a8dca97fc3a68857af","tid":937824,"uid":36492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d17dbda97c78112057dd6f950589c96b692d26","tid":937824,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:45:25.000Z","msg":"你食唔食得涼野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"苦涼野我全家都好ok架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5b1b18d54bf5c960b5fe16b4d08898ef3662af","tid":937824,"uid":33916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"青池夜晚去真係好on9<br />\n好似幻彩 fing long long咁"},{"pid":"f879de0ed578fddd03be96f1535438b01f98efb5","tid":937824,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"book 觀光的士玩一兩粒鐘，自已 set 好行程咪得囉。"},{"pid":"dd93c40344363afd76ec90e4e1b5d12aa3d36379","tid":937824,"uid":6